        {
            "title": "美國眾議院通過共和黨撥款法案 參議院表決料陷入僵局",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"US House Speaker Mike Johnson\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ntubVBaRP9HAKc8P5kjzHg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/03158de7b55b3eda12a740ce65c4bed6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">US House Speaker Mike Johnson</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國眾議院通過臨時撥款法案，以避免政府在10月1日停擺，當天稍晚時段參議院將對法案進行表決，預計民主黨可能因為其中未包含他們要求的醫保支出條款而阻撓法案通過。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">眾議院議長邁克·約翰遜頂住部分共和黨人的抱怨，最終以217票對212票通過這項臨時撥款法案。幾乎所有民主黨眾議員都投下反對票。少數黨領袖Hakeem Jeffries表示，這項法案是「在捍衛美國人醫保與向唐納德·川普屈服之間做出的選擇」。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3839c74a-0367-3974-a317-cc04cbbe2033-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美國眾議院議長邁克·約翰遜攝影師：Al Drago/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/k14PTKi71LTwl_yBVaLcPQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a779a34be3f085ab8028ae1163a67913\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美國眾議院議長邁克·約翰遜攝影師：Al Drago/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">參議院預計在周五稍晚對眾議院版本和民主黨領袖查克·舒默提出的替代法案同時進行表決，後者將把政府資金延長至10月31日。但兩項法案預計都無法表決通過。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題House Passes GOP Funding Bill, Sets Up Senate Shutdown Showdown</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Jack Fitzpatrick、Ken Tran、Maeve Sheehey.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9C%BE%E8%AD%B0%E9%99%A2%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E9%BB%A8%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E9%99%A2%E8%A1%A8%E6%B1%BA%E6%96%99%E9%99%B7%E5%85%A5%E5%83%B5%E5%B1%80-153913544.html",
