        {
            "title": "歐盟提議從2027年起全面禁止進口俄羅斯液化天然氣 較原計畫提前一年",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"635\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/e7zQUr6BzesCSMSeZqgkpQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzNTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e8a7d048dc07a4c940d7b501444edd45\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐盟提議自2027年1月1日起全面禁止進口<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:俄羅斯;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/俄羅斯\">俄羅斯</a>液化天然氣，作為其最新制裁措施的一部分，旨在削弱俄羅斯總統弗拉基米爾·普丁發動對烏克蘭戰爭的能力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐盟還提議對更多俄羅斯銀行和金融機構實施全面交易禁令，並對中國和印度的相關實體實施貿易限制，這些實體曾協助莫斯科繞過歐盟的制裁。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此前，美國總統唐納德·川普呼籲歐盟加強對俄羅斯能源貿易施壓。歐盟原計畫到2027年底逐步淘汰俄羅斯化石燃料。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"烏爾蘇拉·馮德萊恩攝影師：西蒙·沃爾法特/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BWp8qS0nD5QLln5UZIF8sA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e21c4b4a09b86731b73e9bba12846bf6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">烏爾蘇拉·馮德萊恩攝影師：西蒙·沃爾法特/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐盟委員會主席烏爾蘇拉·馮德萊恩周五在布魯塞爾對記者表示，「俄羅斯正充分表現出其對外交和國際法的蔑視。普丁總統屢屢升級局勢 —— 作為回應，歐洲將加大施壓力度。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0631f2b2-9460-354f-90c0-419bcc6a2285-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據歐盟統計局匯編的數據，歐盟每月從俄羅斯進口約5億至7億歐元液化天然氣。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"635\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LAj9IHquVpBdeL2bLb9kLQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzNTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/5502e87b993be96149414432cd036ac2\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題EU Proposes Full Ban on Russian LNG From 2027, a Year Early (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Katharina Rosskopf、Max Ramsay、Andrea Palasciano、Priscila Azevedo Rocha、John Ainger.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E6%8F%90%E8%AD%B0%E5%BE%9E2027%E5%B9%B4%E8%B5%B7%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E6%B6%B2%E5%8C%96%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%B6%E6%B0%A3-%E8%BC%83%E5%8E%9F%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8D-%E5%B9%B4-145518035.html",
