            "title": "iPhone 17開賣｜電訊商出機優惠一覽　csl減逾3000蚊　一間優惠達1.4萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"iPhone 17開賣｜電訊商出機優惠一覽。(資料圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"630\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GEVWVP_mMywRnAvUBAT8lw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/am730_578/708b3d1b2b3f0f239711d57e826e4fb2\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">iPhone 17開賣｜電訊商出機優惠一覽。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">蘋果<span>iPhone 17</span>系列今日(19日)正式開售。除了蘋果官方網站及門店外，本港多家電訊商亦同步開放訂購，並推出多項出機優惠吸引客戶。不過，各電訊商的上台計劃內容及折扣方式不盡相同，消費者在選購前宜仔細比較。《am730》為讀者整合各大電訊商的最新出機優惠，助你輕鬆了解各項計劃詳情，一文睇清點揀最著數。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">iPhone 17入手攻略｜新機價格</h2><table class=\"atom-table w-full mb-module-gap\"><tbody><tr><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\"> </p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">iPhone 17</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">iPhone Air</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">iPhone 17 Pro</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">iPhone 17 Pro Max</p></td></tr><tr><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">256GB</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">6,899港元</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">8,599港元</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">9,399港元</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">10,199港元</p></td></tr><tr><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">512GB</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">8,599港元</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">10,299港元</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">11,099港元</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">11,899港元</p></td></tr><tr><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">1TB</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">-</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">11,999港元</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">12,799港元</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">13,599港元</p></td></tr><tr><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">2TB</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">-</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">-</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">-</p></td><td><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.63] text-px16 lg:leading-[1.8] lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">16,999港元</p></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">iPhone 17入手攻略｜購買連結</h2><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">iPhone 17：<a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:官網連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.apple.com/hk-zh/shop/buy-iphone/iphone-17\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">官網連結</a></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">iPhone Air：<a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:官網連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.apple.com/hk-zh/shop/buy-iphone/iphone-air\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">官網連結</a></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">iPhone 17 Pro及Pro Max：<a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:官網連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.apple.com/hk-zh/shop/buy-iphone/iphone-17-pro\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">官網連結</a></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>iPhone 17</span><span>開賣｜香港寬頻最高折扣1360元</span></span></span></span></span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>香港寬頻(1310)表示，即日起登記指定2.5Gbps GigaFast家居寬頻計劃，可享高達1,360元機價折扣(以購買為iPhone 17 Pro Max 2TB為例)。登記指定流動通訊服務計劃，再送8日旅遊數據日券。要留意，以上優惠只適用於指定住宅地區及安裝服務的地址，於登記前120日內未曾使用香港寬頻的寬頻服務。</span></span></span></span></span></p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c359a482-0fe2-3636-b828-858896d9761e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>此外，</span><span>iPhone 17</span><span>系列亦已於香港寬頻網購平台</span><span>Shoppy </span><span>開放預訂，指定型號可享總值高達</span><span>668</span><span>元</span><span>禮遇，</span><span><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:立即按此瀏覽;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://shoppy.hkbn.net/pages/apple?utm_source=PR&amp;utm_medium=PR&amp;utm_campaign=_20250912_shoppy_2025apple_preorder_promo\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">立即按此瀏覽</a></span><span>。</span></span></span></span></span></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>iPhone 17</span><span>開賣｜中移動</span></span></span></span></span>月費148元以上最高減500元</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>至於中國移動的用戶，如使用148元或以上月費的服務計劃，並加簽12個月合約，便可獲得iPhone出機優惠價，最高折扣500元。</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>若用戶要享受最高優惠，則須選購iPhone Air、iPhone 17 Pro或iPhone 17 Pro Max的最高容量手機。</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>詳情<a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:立即按此瀏覽;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/tc/home/buy-phone/promotions/existing-iphone-promotions\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">立即按此瀏覽</a>。</span></span></span></span></span></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>iPhone 17</span><span>開賣｜SmarTone上台最高減2500元</span></span></span></span></span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>數碼通(SmarTone，315)表示，現凡上台及續約選用指定5G月費計劃，機價直減最高2,500元，兼享專屬預訂禮遇，輕鬆入手最新iPhone。最高折扣須選擇「399月費計劃」並簽24個月合約，每月基本月費399元，另有其他收費。SmarTone又指，上台優惠亦有額外300元Trade-in回贈、指定Apple Watch及AirPods組合500元折扣等。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>SmarTone</span><span>現已於官方網頁</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>接受iPhone 17系列及iPhone Air預訂，並於今年9月19日起正式發售。有關服務計劃詳情，詳情可<a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:按此瀏覽;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.smartone.com/tc/service-site/iPhone17/offer.jsp\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">按此瀏覽</a>。</span></span></span></span></span></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"iPhone 17開賣｜3香港設萬元現金券。(3香港截圖)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"363\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bYtsSPu2s.vLwRcYdPOSuw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTM2NTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/am730_578/a7e8955a80588eca2f99b7fdc9ca034a\" width=\"954\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:954px\">iPhone 17開賣｜3香港設萬元現金券。(3香港截圖)</figcaption></div></figure><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>iPhone 17</span><span>開賣｜3香港設萬元現金券</span></span></span></span></span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>和記電訊香港(215)旗下3香港及尊尚品牌3SUPREME宣布，推出「世界Plan」手機現金券計劃，為選用該計劃的客戶提供總值高達1.4萬元的機價折扣優惠。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>該計劃月費為588元，合約期36個月，全期服務費合共21,168元。客戶可享1萬元手機現金券，現有客戶更可額外獲500元現金券。若撇除現金券價值，實際等同全期服務費為10,668元。</span></span></span></span></span></p><h3 class=\"mb-module-gap text-px20 font-bold lg:text-px18 text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>1.4</span><span>萬元折扣優惠包括：</span></span></span></span></span></h3><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>1</span><span>萬</span><span>元手機現金券(現有客戶額外多500元)，適用於換購年度新機系列</span></span></span></span></span></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>1,600</span><span>元年度新機系列機價折扣</span></span></span></span></span></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>Trade-in</span><span>任何手機型號可享400元額外折扣</span></span></span></span></span></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>贈送2年免費旅遊保險(價值$2,000元)</span></span></span></span></span></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>贈送KABU PASS銀會籍3個月及9折券</span></span></span></span></span></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>憑指定滙豐信用卡上台可獲額外100元月費回贈</span></span></span></span></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>3</span><span>香港及3SUPREME同時宣布全面支援年度新機的eSIM服務。客戶可透過My3 App、3SUPREME App或親臨門市辦理轉換eSIM。3客戶每年可享首三次免費更換eSIM，而3SUPREME客戶則可無限次更換。</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>有關服務計劃詳情，詳情<a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:可按此瀏覽;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://iphone.three.com.hk/website/home/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">可按此瀏覽</a>。</span></span></span></span></span></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>iPhone 17</span><span>開賣｜1O1O及csl上台出機最高可省3200元</span></span></span></span></span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>香港電訊旗下1O1O及csl推出iPhone 17系列專屬上台優惠。現有1O1O、csl、網上行、Now TV及HKT家居電話客戶，只要登記指定1O1O或csl服務計劃，或選用中港澳5G服務計劃，並同時選購iPhone 17系列新機，即可享有最高3,200元手機折扣。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>要享受最高折扣優惠，用戶需選購iPhone 17 Pro Max頂配2TB型號，並搭配150GB、250GB或500GB月費計劃，以及36個月合約期。符合條件後，手機價格可由原價16,999元減至13,799元。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/iphone-17開賣-電訊商出機優惠一覽-csl減逾3000蚊-一間優惠達1.4萬元/600970?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/iphone-17開賣-電訊商出機優惠一覽-csl減逾3000蚊-一間優惠達1.4萬元/600970?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/iphone-17開賣-電訊商出機優惠一覽-csl減逾3000蚊-一間優惠達1.4萬元/600970?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
